  "shortDescription": "🚀 A modern Windows GUI for PyInstaller that helps developers package Python scripts into executable apps with build profiles, live command preview, diagnostics, and release-ready workflows.",
  "description": "⚠️ Requirement\nPython must be installed on your system to use this app.\n\nPyInstaller GUI Builder Pro is a modern Windows desktop tool designed to make Python application packaging easier, faster, and more repeatable. It provides a clean graphical interface for PyInstaller, allowing developers to convert Python scripts into Windows executable applications without manually writing or memorizing complex command-line options.\n\nWhether you are building desktop utilities, automation tools, PyQt/PySide applications, internal business software, or standalone Python-based tools, PyInstaller GUI Builder Pro gives you a structured workflow for configuring, previewing, running, and troubleshooting your builds.\n\nThe app helps you manage packaging options through an intuitive interface, generate accurate PyInstaller commands, save reusable build profiles, review build output in real time, and prepare cleaner release packages for distribution.\n\nWith support for build profiles, hidden imports, additional data files, binary dependencies, output configuration, advanced PyInstaller options, live command preview, build logs, and diagnostic tools, this app is built for developers who want more control over the packaging process while keeping the workflow simple and visual.",
